These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, train
1. the person driving the car is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the train is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday   | june | november |
| Transport     | train    | car   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
There 2 different types of food: spinach, cherry
1. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Transport   | tram | motorbike        |
| Food      | spinach  | cherry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Pet   | turtle    | guinea-pig |
| Sport   | water-polo | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, lilac
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, may
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Color   | blood-red      | lilac |
| Birthday       | november | may    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, siglo
1. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet           | ferret | mouse |
| Cigar   | siglo    | alhambra         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
City: hamburg, edinburgh
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| City       | edinburgh | hamburg  |
| Hobby   | collecting  | woodworking |

 #################################

 
