.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, snowboarding
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Sport   | snowboarding       | golf   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | cola |

